---
import Main from '../layouts/main.astro'
---

<Main title='Method'>
  <div class="bg-white">
    <div class="mx-auto max-w-7xl py-24 sm:py-32 sm:px-2 lg:px-4">
      <div class="mx-auto max-w-2xl px-4 lg:max-w-none">
        <div class="max-w-3xl">
          <h2 class="font-semibold text-purple-500">From idea to execution</h2>
          <p class="mt-2 text-3xl font-bold tracking-tight text-gray-900 sm:text-4xl">
            You have an idea!
          </p>
          <p class="mt-4 text-gray-500">
            What next? How will your product vision to your developers? How do you make sure the final delivery serves your vision? Here is our method to figuring that out.
          </p>
        </div>
        
        <div class="relative mt-24">
          <div class="absolute inset-0 flex items-center" aria-hidden="true">
            <div class="w-full border-t border-gray-300"></div>
          </div>
          <div class="relative flex justify-center">
            <span class="bg-white px-3 text-lg font-medium text-gray-900">Scoping</span>
          </div>
        </div>
  
        <div class="mt-10 space-y-16 pt-10 sm:mt-8 sm:pt-8">
          <div class="flex flex-col-reverse lg:grid lg:grid-cols-12 lg:items-center lg:gap-x-8">
            <div class="mt-6 lg:col-span-5 lg:mt-0 xl:col-span-4">
              <h3 class="text-lg font-medium text-purple-600">Adventure-ready</h3>
              <p class="mt-2 text-sm text-gray-500">The Drawstring Canister is water and tear resistant with durable canvas construction. This bag holds up to the demands of daily use while keeping your snacks secure.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="flex-auto lg:col-span-7 xl:col-span-8">
              <div class="aspect-w-5 aspect-h-2 overflow-hidden rounded-lg bg-gray-100">
                <img src="https://tailwindui.com/img/ecommerce-images/product-feature-04-detail-03.jpg" alt="Printed photo of bag being tossed into the sky on top of grass." class="object-cover object-center">
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
          
          <div class="relative">
            <div class="absolute inset-0 flex items-center" aria-hidden="true">
              <div class="w-full border-t border-gray-300"></div>
            </div>
            <div class="relative flex justify-center">
              <span class="bg-white px-3 text-lg font-medium text-gray-900">Wireframe</span>
            </div>
          </div>
  
          <div class="flex flex-col-reverse lg:grid lg:grid-cols-12 lg:items-center lg:gap-x-8">
            <div class="mt-6 lg:col-span-5 lg:mt-0 xl:col-span-4">
              <h3 class="text-lg font-medium text-purple-600">Minimal and clean</h3>
              <p class="mt-2 text-sm text-gray-500">Everything you need, nothing you don&#039;t. This bag has the simple, contemporary design that enables you to tell everyone you know about how essentialism is the only rational way to live life.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="flex-auto lg:col-span-7 xl:col-span-8">
              <div class="aspect-w-5 aspect-h-2 overflow-hidden rounded-lg bg-gray-100">
                <img src="https://tailwindui.com/img/ecommerce-images/product-feature-04-detail-01.jpg" alt="Double stitched black canvas hook loop." class="object-cover object-center">
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
  
          <div class="flex flex-col-reverse lg:grid lg:grid-cols-12 lg:items-center lg:gap-x-8">
            <div class="mt-6 lg:col-span-5 lg:mt-0 xl:col-span-4">
              <h3 class="text-lg font-medium text-purple-600">Organized</h3>
              <p class="mt-2 text-sm text-gray-500">Never lose your snacks again with our patent-pending snack stash pocket system. With dedicated pouches for each of your snacking needs, the Drawstring Canister unlocks new levels of efficiency and convenience.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="flex-auto lg:col-span-7 xl:col-span-8">
              <div class="aspect-w-5 aspect-h-2 overflow-hidden rounded-lg bg-gray-100">
                <img src="https://tailwindui.com/img/ecommerce-images/product-feature-04-detail-02.jpg" alt="Black canvas body with chrome zipper and key ring." class="object-cover object-center">
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
          
          <div class="relative">
            <div class="absolute inset-0 flex items-center" aria-hidden="true">
              <div class="w-full border-t border-gray-300"></div>
            </div>
            <div class="relative flex justify-center">
              <span class="bg-white px-3 text-lg font-medium text-gray-900">Solution Architecture</span>
            </div>
          </div>
  
          <div class="flex flex-col-reverse lg:grid lg:grid-cols-12 lg:items-center lg:gap-x-8">
            <div class="mt-6 lg:col-span-5 lg:mt-0 xl:col-span-4">
              <h3 class="text-lg font-medium text-purple-600">Minimal and clean</h3>
              <p class="mt-2 text-sm text-gray-500">Everything you need, nothing you don&#039;t. This bag has the simple, contemporary design that enables you to tell everyone you know about how essentialism is the only rational way to live life.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="flex-auto lg:col-span-7 xl:col-span-8">
              <div class="aspect-w-5 aspect-h-2 overflow-hidden rounded-lg bg-gray-100">
                <img src="https://tailwindui.com/img/ecommerce-images/product-feature-04-detail-01.jpg" alt="Double stitched black canvas hook loop." class="object-cover object-center">
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
  <div class="relative bg-white py-32">
    <div class="absolute inset-x-0 top-0 hidden h-1/2 bg-gradient-to-b from-gray-100 lg:block" aria-hidden="true"></div>
    <div class="mx-auto max-w-7xl bg-purple-600 lg:bg-transparent lg:px-8">
      <div class="lg:grid lg:grid-cols-12">
        <div class="relative z-10 lg:col-span-4 lg:col-start-1 lg:row-start-1 lg:bg-transparent lg:py-16">
          <div class="absolute inset-x-0 h-1/2 bg-gray-50 lg:hidden" aria-hidden="true"></div>
          <div class="mx-auto max-w-md px-4 sm:max-w-3xl sm:px-6 lg:max-w-none lg:p-0">
            <div class="aspect-w-10 aspect-h-6 sm:aspect-w-2 sm:aspect-h-1 lg:aspect-w-1">
              <img class="rounded-3xl object-cover object-center shadow-2xl" src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1507207611509-ec012433ff52?ixlib=rb-1.2.1&ixid=MXwxMjA3fDB8MHxwaG90by1wYWdlfHx8fGVufDB8fHw%3D&auto=format&fit=crop&w=934&q=80" alt="">
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
  
        <div class="relative bg-purple-600 lg:col-span-10 lg:col-start-3 lg:row-start-1 lg:grid lg:grid-cols-10 lg:items-center lg:rounded-3xl">
          <div class="absolute inset-0 hidden overflow-hidden rounded-3xl lg:block" aria-hidden="true">
            <svg class="absolute bottom-full left-full translate-y-1/3 -translate-x-2/3 transform xl:bottom-auto xl:top-0 xl:translate-y-0" width="404" height="384" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 404 384" aria-hidden="true">
              <defs>
                <pattern id="64e643ad-2176-4f86-b3d7-f2c5da3b6a6d" x="0" y="0" width="20" height="20" patternUnits="userSpaceOnUse">
                  <rect x="0" y="0" width="4" height="4" class="text-purple-500" fill="currentColor" />
                </pattern>
              </defs>
              <rect width="404" height="384" fill="url(#64e643ad-2176-4f86-b3d7-f2c5da3b6a6d)" />
            </svg>
            <svg class="absolute top-full -translate-y-1/3 -translate-x-1/3 transform xl:-translate-y-1/2" width="404" height="384" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 404 384" aria-hidden="true">
              <defs>
                <pattern id="64e643ad-2176-4f86-b3d7-f2c5da3b6a6d" x="0" y="0" width="20" height="20" patternUnits="userSpaceOnUse">
                  <rect x="0" y="0" width="4" height="4" class="text-purple-500" fill="currentColor" />
                </pattern>
              </defs>
              <rect width="404" height="384" fill="url(#64e643ad-2176-4f86-b3d7-f2c5da3b6a6d)" />
            </svg>
          </div>
          <div class="relative mx-auto max-w-md space-y-6 py-12 px-4 sm:max-w-3xl sm:py-16 sm:px-6 lg:col-span-6 lg:col-start-4 lg:max-w-none lg:p-0">
            <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold tracking-tight text-white" id="join-heading">Join our team</h2>
            <p class="text-lg text-white">Varius facilisi mauris sed sit. Non sed et duis dui leo, vulputate id malesuada non. Cras aliquet purus dui laoreet diam sed lacus, fames.</p>
            <a class="block w-full rounded-md border border-transparent bg-white py-3 px-5 text-center text-base font-medium text-purple-700 shadow-md hover:bg-gray-50 sm:inline-block sm:w-auto" href="#">Explore open positions</a>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</Main>